{"version":3,"term":{"cols":92,"rows":28},"timestamp":1783185105,"idle_time_limit":1.4,"command":"SKIP_BUILD=1 IRONCLAW_ENGAGE_TIMEOUT=120 examples/live-containment/run.sh --attach","title":"IronClaw live-containment: a jailbroken agent tries to escape, the box holds","env":{"SHELL":"/bin/zsh"}}
[0.024, "o", "==> waiting for the control-plane to be ready (up to 90s)"]
[0.028, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "==> engaging a live sandbox: chatting to 'mock-agent' so its per-session container launches\r\n"]
[0.045, "o", "==> waiting for the sandbox to come up (up to 120s)"]
[0.104, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "==============================================================================\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", " \u001b[1mIronClaw live containment\u001b[0m — a fully-jailbroken agent tries to break out\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", " sandbox under test: \u001b[1mic-sbx-ses_b392cddfd4f8c046\u001b[0m   (runc fallback for the laptop demo)\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "==============================================================================\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[36m[1/3] Exfiltrate stolen data to the attacker\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m    agent (inside the box, uid 65532) runs:\u001b[0m \u001b[33mgetent hosts api.anthropic.com   # resolve C2, then POST the loot\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.435, "o", "    \u001b[32m\u001b[1m⛔ BLOCKED\u001b[0m\u001b[32m — no network namespace: only `lo` exists (interfaces: lo), DNS resolution fails. network=none.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[1m\u001b[36m[2/3] Read the operator's host filesystem\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m    agent (inside the box, uid 65532) runs:\u001b[0m \u001b[33mcat /host/etc/shadow /etc/ironclaw-host-marker   # steal host secrets\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.280, "o", "    \u001b[32m\u001b[1m⛔ BLOCKED\u001b[0m\u001b[32m — host root is outside the sandbox mount namespace: the paths do not exist in the box.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n\u001b[1m\u001b[36m[3/3] Seize the host via the Docker Engine socket\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\u001b[2m    agent (inside the box, uid 65532) runs:\u001b[0m \u001b[33mdocker -H unix:///var/run/docker.sock run --privileged ...   # own the host\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.411, "o", "    \u001b[32m\u001b[1m⛔ BLOCKED\u001b[0m\u001b[32m — the Engine socket is never mounted in and there is no docker client: nothing to seize.\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "==============================================================================\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", " \u001b[32m\u001b[1mCONTAINMENT SUMMARY: 3/3 escape attempts DENIED. The box held.\u001b[0m\r\n==============================================================================\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", " A fully-compromised agent could not phone home, could not read the host, and\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", " could not seize the Engine. That is \u001b[1misolation you can prove, not just promise.\u001b[0m\r\n\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", " Next: the full six-assertion battery + signed containment report ->\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "   \u001b[1mexamples/red-team-escape/run.sh\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.000, "o", "   Production seals each session with gVisor and network=none (docs/breaking-our-own-sandbox.md).\r\n"]
[0.000, "x", "0"]
